You could have used it before with a gif tunnel. That&#x27;s the way I&#x27;ve been doing 6rd on vanilla FreeBSD without any 6rd support.<p>edit:<p>Here&#x27;s what you put in rc.conf<p><pre><code>  cloned_interfaces=&quot;gif0&quot;
  ipv6_activate_all_interfaces=&quot;YES&quot;
  ifconfig_gif0=&quot;tunnel $MYIPv4 $THEIRIPv4&quot;
  ifconfig_gif0_ipv6=&quot;inet6 alias $MYIPv6 $THEIRIPv6 prefixlen 128&quot;
  ipv6_defaultrouter=&quot;$THEIRIPv6 -mtu 1280&quot;</code></pre>
